:"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","title":"Components","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/presentationDetents(_:selection:)":{"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/presentationdetents(_:selection:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"presentationDetents","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text"